												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[ZEVLOR] Hearing the crowd start to chatter behind him, turns to see what their looking at., [HALSIN] Steps in from the shadows and walks into the Den. He acknowldges the gathered Tieflings, but continues forward toward the Grove., [CROWD] Small clusters of Tieflings talking, packing for their journey. They catch sight of Halsin, and call out or wave to him, happy to see he's back., <CMitchell>"
												}
